'''艾薇·安德森'''（{{lang-en|Ever Gabo Anderson}}，{{bd|2007年|11月3日}}<ref>{{Cite web|title=MillaJ.com :: The Official Milla Jovovich Website :: From Milla November 2007|url=http://www.millaj.com/from/1107.shtml|access-date=2020-11-24|website=www.millaj.com|archive-date=2020-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200209121512/http://millaj.com/from/1107.shtml}}</ref>），美國童星，女性模特兒。

==早年生活==
艾薇的母親是著名女星[[蜜拉·喬娃維琪|蜜拉·喬娃維琪]]，父親是英藉導演[[保羅·W·S·安德森|保羅·W·S·安德森]]，她得到雙親的鼓勵在娛樂圈發展<ref name=People>{{Cite web|title=Milla Jovovich's Daughter Ever, 12, Opens Up About Having to 'Prove' Herself in Hollywood|url=https://people.com/parents/milla-jovovich-daughter-ever-proving-herself-hollywood-acting-flaunt-magazine/|access-date=2020-11-24|website=PEOPLE.com|language=EN|archive-date=2020-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200421235709/https://people.com/parents/milla-jovovich-daughter-ever-proving-herself-hollywood-acting-flaunt-magazine/}}</ref>。

==事業==
艾薇在9歲時為兒童版[[时尚_(Vogue)|時尚雜誌]]當封面模特兒<ref name="Bear">{{cite web |last1=Bear |first1=BJ Panda |title=Ever Anderson: An Articulation |url=https://flaunt.com/content/ever-anderson |website=Flaunt Magazine |access-date=1 December 2020 |date=10 April 2020}}</ref>，初登銀幕是2016年，在其父親執導電影《[[惡靈古堡：最終章|惡靈古堡：最終章]]》中飾演兒時的[[艾莉絲_(惡靈古堡)|艾莉絲·馬庫斯]]（成年角色由她的母親飾演）<ref>{{cite web |title=Ever Anderson |url=https://www.interviewmagazine.com/film/ever-anderson |website=Interview Magazine |access-date=1 December 2020 |date=6 December 2016}}</ref>。她在《[[黑寡婦_(電影)|黑寡婦]]》亦飾演女主角[[黑寡妇_(娜塔莎·罗曼诺娃)|娜塔莎·羅曼諾娃]]的孩童角色<ref>{{Cite web|last1=March 11|first1=Skyler Shuler on|last2=2020|date=2020-03-11|title=Disney's Live-Action 'Peter Pan' Finds Their Peter Pan and Wendy|url=https://thedisinsider.com/2020/03/11/disneys-live-action-peter-pan-peter-pan-and-wendy/|access-date=2020-11-24|website=The DisInsider|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929095258/https://thedisinsider.com/2020/03/11/disneys-live-action-peter-pan-peter-pan-and-wendy/}}</ref>。

